node.text: We’re so excited that Vance gets to enjoy online learning from home 😍 #ad After having kids *and playing teacher to the boys*, my gratitude for teachers has increased even more! So this fall @amazon and I are helping teachers  go back to school with a smile! Amazon is  supporting #ClearTheList, a movement that encourages customers to give back to teachers by purchasing needed school supplies from their Amazon Wish Lists. Do you know a deserving teacher with an Amazon Wish List? Leave the link in the comments! Let’s team up and support our teachers!!!❤️ #PrimeLife
